        WTI enables data standardization for AI solutions and delivers data management solutions that integrate, protect, enhance and add value to digital information assets.
      </p> -->
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="#capabilities" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium border-2 border-transparent hover:bg-transparent hover:text-white hover:border-white transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105" style="animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 1s both;">
          Capabilities
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 